From: Marco Grandis <grandis@dima.unige.it>
Subject: categories: Preprint available: Collared cospans, cohomotopy and TQFT
Date: Wed, 2 May 2007 11:47:48 +0200
To: categories@mta.ca
Sender: cat-dist@mta.ca
