From: "Zinovy Diskin" <zdiskin@cs.toronto.edu>
Subject: categories: Re: hyperdoctrines and cylindric algebras (Correction)
To: categories <categories@mta.ca>
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=ISO-8859-1; format=flowed
